{
  "stem": "5430.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the other place, tons of sugar, but hard to transport one to the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Our people were able to do that and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So from that point on, we were able to wheel and deal, so to speak, in different products, merchandise.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not that I wanted, I had no choice, because they wanted me to be in the labor front, and I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So once I run away from them, I had no papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, yeah, with family or whenever we heard they're coming to look for-- not just for me, I mean personally, but for-- I wasn't the only one to run away.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were always looking for the guys that were neither in the army or in the labor front.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only among our-- well, we managed to bribe some of the [INAUDIBLE] in a local level to look away, in other words, and not bother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A couple years.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was illegal from that point on, which is till 1945 or the beginning of '46.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During that time, we found out that our father was released from prison over there, because he was totally emaciated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother Sam and my sister went to visit him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the merchandise that they had was some fruit from the south, which was like gold over-- up north.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were able to, for an apple or a pear or an orange or something like that, they-- they could make their way through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eventually, they managed to get him released, and-- I mean, he was released, and to get him a permit to travel to join the family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1944?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Late '43 or '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we stayed till the-- till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we heard news.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
